OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSwiss shock at Davos sign  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsaying no skis for Jews    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Swiss police have opened an            
OL,6, investigation into a ski hire shop's   
OL,7, announcement it would no longer rent   
OL,8, skis and sledges to Jewish customers.  
OL,10,FThe shop, in the famous resort of      
OL,11,FDavos, has now reversed its decision.  
OL,13,FIt has taken down the signs, translated
OL,14,Finto Hebrew, which informed customers  
OL,15,Fof the ban.                            
OL,17,FBut many have argued the case is a     
OL,18,Fclear violation of Switzerland's laws  
OL,19,Fagainst discrimination and incitement  
OL,20,Fto racial or religious hatred.         
